1
00:00:09,187 --> 00:00:09,983
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16,328 --> 00:00:18,956
<i>Running like a fugitive,</i>

3
00:00:19,998 --> 00:00:22,159
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23,835 --> 00:00:26,497
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27,606 --> 00:00:30,234
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:31,943 --> 00:00:35,037
<i>For no single one,</i>

7
00:00:35,547 --> 00:00:38,812
<i>To none does belong,</i>

8
00:00:40,285 --> 00:00:44,551
<i>This time is ours, right now...</i>

9
00:00:47,192 --> 00:00:49,057
<i>Unraveling the pain,</i>

10
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:50,889
<i>Unraveling our hearts,</i>

11
00:00:50,962 --> 00:00:53,294
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54,833 --> 00:00:56,596
<i>Stifling our breath,</i>

13
00:00:56,668 --> 00:00:58,568
<i>Reaching for beyond,</i>

14
00:00:58,637 --> 00:01:01,071
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:02,974 --> 00:01:09,538
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10,515 --> 00:01:13,143
<i>To the distant light above,</i>

17
00:01:13,585 --> 00:01:16,782
<i>Yes, we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21,526 --> 00:01:22,823
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25,397 --> 00:01:26,921
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:02:26,469 --> 00:02:29,267
What's with you?!

21
00:02:57,366 --> 00:03:03,327
<i>Battle on the Bridge! Zabuza Returns!</i>

22
00:03:10,346 --> 00:03:12,075
Good morning!

23
00:03:17,553 --> 00:03:18,144
Here.

24
00:03:18,754 --> 00:03:19,584
Thank you.

25
00:03:25,761 --> 00:03:28,958
Naruto didn't come back
last night, either?

26
00:03:29,198 --> 00:03:30,495
He's such a fool,

27
00:03:30,733 --> 00:03:32,724
he's been out every night,
climbing trees.

28
00:03:33,602 --> 00:03:37,595
He might be dead already
from using up too much Chakra.

29
00:03:38,407 --> 00:03:40,238
I wonder if Naruto's okay.

30
00:03:40,743 --> 00:03:43,234
To think a child's out in
the middle of the night.

31
00:03:43,846 --> 00:03:45,939
Well, you don't need to worry.

32
00:03:46,215 --> 00:03:48,979
Although he may not seem to be,
he's a full fledged Ninja.

33
00:03:49,552 --> 00:03:50,610
I wonder...

34
00:03:51,153 --> 00:03:55,453
That idiot's probably
all pooped out right about now.

35
00:03:59,929 --> 00:04:00,793
Sasuke?

36
00:04:03,499 --> 00:04:04,329
I'm going for a walk.

37
00:04:05,501 --> 00:04:06,866
But we're about to eat...

38
00:04:10,139 --> 00:04:10,833
That was fast!

39
00:04:39,034 --> 00:04:41,764
You'll catch a cold if
you keep sleeping here.

40
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,507
Who're you?

41
00:04:54,683 --> 00:05:00,383
Uh... Did you wake me up, sis?
I mean, what're you doing here?

42
00:05:00,990 --> 00:05:02,116
I'm gathering medicinal herbs.

43
00:05:03,025 --> 00:05:04,219
Herbs?

44
00:05:04,493 --> 00:05:08,395
Yes. For healing injuries,
sickness and the like.

45
00:05:17,273 --> 00:05:19,503
You got a lot to do early
in the morning, sis...

46
00:05:19,909 --> 00:05:21,001
You, too.

47
00:05:21,176 --> 00:05:23,838
What've you been doing
in a place like this so early?

48
00:05:25,781 --> 00:05:26,873
Training!

49
00:05:29,652 --> 00:05:33,247
Could it be that...
you're a Ninja or something?

50
00:05:34,657 --> 00:05:36,557
What with that headband and...

51
00:05:36,859 --> 00:05:38,724
Is that what I look like? Is it?

52
00:05:39,228 --> 00:05:40,957
Yup! I'm a Ninja!

53
00:05:42,197 --> 00:05:45,655
No kidding.
You're great, aren't you.

54
00:05:48,137 --> 00:05:51,664
But... why are you training?

55
00:05:52,074 --> 00:05:54,599
As for me,
I want to get stronger!

56
00:05:55,477 --> 00:05:58,810
But, you already look
strong enough.

57
00:05:58,881 --> 00:06:02,146
No, no! I want to get
even stronger!

58
00:06:04,486 --> 00:06:06,852
What for?

59
00:06:07,256 --> 00:06:09,781
To become the best Ninja
in my village!

60
00:06:10,392 --> 00:06:13,190
I'm going to get everyone
to recognize my strength!

61
00:06:13,729 --> 00:06:17,165
And I have to prove something
to a certain person!

62
00:06:18,634 --> 00:06:24,266
Is that for the sake of somebody?
Or is it for your own sake?

63
00:06:25,207 --> 00:06:25,866
Huh?

64
00:06:28,410 --> 00:06:30,173
What's so funny?!

65
00:06:32,047 --> 00:06:34,845
Do you have somebody
precious in your life?

66
00:06:35,985 --> 00:06:37,077
Precious?

67
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,779
What is it you want to say, sis?

68
00:08:20,823 --> 00:08:21,721
<i>What is it?</i>

69
00:08:22,491 --> 00:08:27,121
When a person has something
precious they want to protect...

70
00:08:27,763 --> 00:08:29,993
that's when they can truly
become strong.

71
00:08:36,105 --> 00:08:39,700
Your dad loves the town
you're from, so...

72
00:08:40,042 --> 00:08:43,910
I absolutely won't allow
my comrades to get killed!

73
00:08:45,747 --> 00:08:48,682
Get your hands off Iruka Sensei!

74
00:08:49,751 --> 00:08:50,649
I'll kill you!!

75
00:08:51,854 --> 00:08:54,789
Yeah! I know that well, too!

76
00:09:00,295 --> 00:09:02,058
You'll get strong.

77
00:09:02,331 --> 00:09:02,888
Yeah!

78
00:09:03,599 --> 00:09:06,500
I hope we meet again somewhere.

79
00:09:08,303 --> 00:09:09,895
Oh... and...

80
00:09:11,273 --> 00:09:12,535
I'm a man!

81
00:09:14,143 --> 00:09:17,442
<i>That can't be!</i>
<i>He's cuter than Sakura.</i>

82
00:09:46,808 --> 00:09:48,799
Why? That's strange.

83
00:09:49,011 --> 00:09:51,070
This world is full of mystery...

84
00:09:51,413 --> 00:09:53,813
Ouch.
Hey! What're you doing?!

85
00:09:54,016 --> 00:09:57,144
Did you forget about mealtime,
you idiot?

86
00:10:03,192 --> 00:10:04,250
Naruto?

87
00:10:08,597 --> 00:10:10,497
What in the world is Naruto doing?

88
00:10:10,999 --> 00:10:14,093
And Sasuke hasn't come back
from his walk either...

89
00:10:21,677 --> 00:10:25,204
No way...
Naruto can climb that high now?

90
00:10:26,381 --> 00:10:27,143
Wow!

91
00:10:29,351 --> 00:10:30,613
How'bout that, how'bout that?!

92
00:10:30,752 --> 00:10:33,550
As for me,
I can climb this high now!

93
00:10:37,626 --> 00:10:38,183
Whoa!

94
00:10:40,128 --> 00:10:40,924
Oh, you idiot!

95
00:10:41,330 --> 00:10:41,853
This is bad!

96
00:10:47,536 --> 00:10:49,060
Gotcha!

97
00:10:51,106 --> 00:10:52,835
You fell for it, you fell for it!

98
00:10:55,010 --> 00:10:57,069
Don't scare us like that!

99
00:10:58,013 --> 00:11:00,538
I'll kill him later! Cha!

100
00:11:01,550 --> 00:11:03,518
<i>He's grown a little, eh.</i>

101
00:11:07,990 --> 00:11:09,287
Oh! You idiot, Naruto!

102
00:11:09,591 --> 00:11:11,183
It's cuz you went overboard!

103
00:11:21,470 --> 00:11:23,438
You fool.

104
00:11:24,873 --> 00:11:25,862
Sasuke...?

105
00:11:26,742 --> 00:11:28,937
Nice, Sasuke.
You're awesome!

106
00:11:30,445 --> 00:11:33,642
<i>These kids are really growing.</i>

107
00:11:48,196 --> 00:11:49,094
Naruto...

108
00:11:50,265 --> 00:11:51,254
Uzumaki, eh.

109
00:11:59,474 --> 00:12:01,567
You've recovered considerably.

110
00:12:02,444 --> 00:12:03,240
All right...

111
00:12:04,012 --> 00:12:05,912
Just a little more, Haku.

112
00:12:06,615 --> 00:12:07,172
Yes.

113
00:12:24,070 --> 00:12:24,968
Shall we go back?

114
00:12:25,672 --> 00:12:26,297
Okay!

115
00:12:31,745 --> 00:12:33,212
They're late.

116
00:12:33,446 --> 00:12:35,676
And not just Naruto,
but even Sasuke too.

117
00:12:41,121 --> 00:12:42,554
What happened to you guys?

118
00:12:42,622 --> 00:12:44,749
You're really muddy
and really wiped out.

119
00:12:46,559 --> 00:12:49,790
We both... climbed up to the top.

120
00:12:50,997 --> 00:12:51,486
Good.

121
00:12:53,166 --> 00:12:57,796
Naruto, Sasuke, you'll also start guarding
Tazuna next time!

122
00:12:58,905 --> 00:13:00,236
Got it! Whoa!

123
00:13:01,207 --> 00:13:02,231
You idiot!

124
00:13:05,912 --> 00:13:09,439
In just a teeny little bit,
the bridge will be complete.

125
00:13:09,749 --> 00:13:11,273
It's thanks to you guys.

126
00:13:11,551 --> 00:13:13,712
Even so, don't let your guard down...

127
00:13:15,088 --> 00:13:18,182
I've really wanted to ask
you for a long time now...

128
00:13:19,392 --> 00:13:23,920
But why are you still here
even though I lied about the mission?

129
00:13:26,666 --> 00:13:29,658
To see what is right without doing it
bespeaks an absence of courage.

130
00:13:29,736 --> 00:13:32,136
Like master, like man.

131
00:13:35,942 --> 00:13:38,137
It's a teaching of the late Hokage.

132
00:14:05,839 --> 00:14:07,204
The things I truly
hold dear to myself...

133
00:14:07,273 --> 00:14:09,833
I'll protect until the very end
with both these arms.

134
00:14:12,912 --> 00:14:14,812
Don't cry... Inari.

135
00:14:26,459 --> 00:14:27,084
Why...?

136
00:14:29,362 --> 00:14:30,454
What is it?

137
00:14:32,799 --> 00:14:35,666
Why do you desperately work so hard
until you get like that?!

138
00:14:35,802 --> 00:14:39,465
There's no way you'd be
a match for Gato's men even if you train!

139
00:14:40,673 --> 00:14:43,471
No matter what cool things you say
or how much effort you make...

140
00:14:43,877 --> 00:14:45,902
the weak always lose out...

141
00:14:45,979 --> 00:14:48,607
against the truly strong!

142
00:14:54,354 --> 00:14:58,381
Shut up. I'm not like you.

143
00:14:58,525 --> 00:15:01,585
Shut up!
Looking at you makes me sick!

144
00:15:01,661 --> 00:15:04,892
Sticking your nose in even though
you know nothing of this land!

145
00:15:05,598 --> 00:15:07,793
I'm not like you who's always
acting frivolous

146
00:15:07,867 --> 00:15:10,131
not knowing one thing about pain!

147
00:15:12,806 --> 00:15:17,470
So you're just gonna cry
all day like the lead in a tragedy?

148
00:15:18,578 --> 00:15:23,140
An idiot like you can just cry forever!
You crybaby!

149
00:15:25,018 --> 00:15:27,043
Naruto! That's a bit harsh!

150
00:15:31,858 --> 00:15:32,688
Naruto...

151
00:15:54,747 --> 00:15:56,408
Got a minute?

152
00:16:04,724 --> 00:16:07,818
Naruto didn't mean any harm
with what he said...

153
00:16:09,295 --> 00:16:11,263
He's just uncouth, so...

154
00:16:14,534 --> 00:16:18,026
We heard the story
about your father from Tazuna.

155
00:16:19,272 --> 00:16:23,641
Like you, Naruto never had
a father as a young child...

156
00:16:25,078 --> 00:16:27,569
Actually he doesn't know either
of his parents.

157
00:16:28,214 --> 00:16:31,047
Not only that.
He didn't have a single friend.

158
00:16:31,317 --> 00:16:31,806
What?

159
00:16:32,852 --> 00:16:33,750
However...

160
00:16:34,087 --> 00:16:37,454
I've never seen him sulk,
be timid, or cry.

161
00:16:38,925 --> 00:16:44,295
He's always eager,
wanting to be acknowledged by someone.

162
00:16:45,231 --> 00:16:48,928
If it's for the sake of that "dream,"
he always risks his life.

163
00:16:52,405 --> 00:16:55,704
He's probably tired of crying.

164
00:17:03,349 --> 00:17:06,409
So, he knows the true meaning
of the word strong.

165
00:17:08,588 --> 00:17:10,715
Like your father.

166
00:17:11,891 --> 00:17:15,987
Naruto might understand your feelings
the most.

167
00:17:18,031 --> 00:17:19,760
What Naruto said earlier...

168
00:17:20,466 --> 00:17:25,665
There's no mistaking that
he's told himself that over and over again.

169
00:17:38,651 --> 00:17:41,017
Okay, then!
I leave Naruto in your hands.

170
00:17:44,157 --> 00:17:46,387
Because he's used his body
to the limit...

171
00:17:47,527 --> 00:17:50,052
I don't think he'll be able
to move today.

172
00:17:51,364 --> 00:17:54,333
Mr. Kakashi, are you feeling all right?

173
00:17:54,567 --> 00:17:55,898
Yes, somehow.

174
00:17:56,469 --> 00:17:57,834
We'll be going!

175
00:18:03,810 --> 00:18:05,437
What're you doing?

176
00:18:05,578 --> 00:18:08,411
I didn't hire you guys for charity work...

177
00:18:08,748 --> 00:18:11,342
<i>Hey, are you listening, Zabuza?!</i>
<i>Hey!!</i>

178
00:18:15,822 --> 00:18:17,813
Shall we go... Haku?

179
00:18:18,491 --> 00:18:19,014
Yes.

180
00:18:34,607 --> 00:18:35,665
I overslept!

181
00:18:37,644 --> 00:18:39,839
Hey hey!! Where is everyone?

182
00:18:40,713 --> 00:18:44,911
Naruto. Your Sensei wanted you
to rest and relax... today

183
00:18:46,552 --> 00:18:47,177
I knew it.

184
00:18:47,553 --> 00:18:48,952
They left me behind.

185
00:18:52,625 --> 00:18:53,421
I'll be back.

186
00:19:02,101 --> 00:19:04,467
Darn it!
They could've woken me up!

187
00:19:14,113 --> 00:19:16,172
W-What the heck is this?!

188
00:19:23,156 --> 00:19:26,319
What is going on?
What's happened?

189
00:19:27,193 --> 00:19:28,125
<i>It couldn't be...</i>

190
00:19:29,762 --> 00:19:31,593
Inari! Give me a hand.

191
00:19:32,398 --> 00:19:33,228
Inari!?

192
00:19:33,566 --> 00:19:34,692
I'll be right there.

193
00:19:51,217 --> 00:19:51,945
<i>This mist...</i>

194
00:19:52,685 --> 00:19:55,085
Sasuke! Sakura!
They're coming!

195
00:20:00,593 --> 00:20:02,390
<i>I knew he was still alive.</i>

196
00:20:03,329 --> 00:20:04,921
<i>Making an appearance so soon, eh...</i>

197
00:20:05,465 --> 00:20:06,659
Say, Kakashi Sensei.

198
00:20:06,966 --> 00:20:09,935
This is his... Hidden Mist Jutsu, right?!

199
00:20:16,743 --> 00:20:18,802
Sorry to have kept you waiting, Kakashi.

200
00:20:19,579 --> 00:20:22,480
I see you've got those brats
with you as always.

201
00:20:23,583 --> 00:20:27,314
He's still trembling. Poor thing.

202
00:20:37,230 --> 00:20:39,528
I'm trembling with... excitement.

203
00:20:41,667 --> 00:20:43,430
Do it, Sasuke.

204
00:20:55,414 --> 00:20:56,346
<i>I can see it!</i>

205
00:20:57,617 --> 00:21:00,586
Well well. So he could
see the Water Clones, eh.

206
00:21:00,953 --> 00:21:03,353
That brat's grown quite a bit.

207
00:21:04,557 --> 00:21:06,957
This means a rival has emerged, Haku.

208
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:08,925
So it seems.

209
00:22:52,583 --> 00:22:55,916
Phew, that was a close shave.

210
00:22:56,220 --> 00:23:00,054
Sorry I was late.
But Inari, you were great.

211
00:23:00,624 --> 00:23:04,025
I was able to save your mom
thanks to your courage.

212
00:23:04,261 --> 00:23:05,592
Hey, wait a minute.

213
00:23:05,830 --> 00:23:07,661
Doesn't the fact that
we were attacked mean

214
00:23:07,732 --> 00:23:10,166
that Kakashi Sensei and
the others are in danger too?!

215
00:23:11,035 --> 00:23:13,731
Next episode:
"Haku's Secret Jutsu: Crystal Ice Mirrors"

216
00:23:13,938 --> 00:23:16,498
I'm going to kick butt once again!
